Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st1403 Description

ST 1403 SARMI Threshold Metadata Sets.

This standard defines the Synthetic Aperture Radar Motion Imagery (SARMI) threshold metadata which enable the basic capabilities of Situational Awareness, Discovery and Retrieval, and Cross-Domain Dissemination. This metadata is intended to convey collection information related to the SAR image formation and SAR coherent change product processes used to create the SARMI data in addition to mission and classification information. SAR Motion Imagery Metadata.
